ision-to-delay-arms-shipments-could-impact-idfs-readiness-on-other-fronts/0000018f-5ad4-d9a0-a38f-fef7551e0000</guid></item><item><title>控制拉法口岸意味着以色列再次占领加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/taking-control-of-the-rafah-crossing-means-that-israel-is-once-against-occupying-gaza/0000018f-5ae3-d9a0-a38f-fee787130000</link><description>从以色列的角度来看，此举具有军事合理性，根据国际法可能会产生影响，并可能使耶路撒冷与开罗的关系复杂化</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/taking-control-of-the-rafah-crossing-means-that-israel-is-once-against-occupying-gaza/0000018f-5ae3-d9a0-a38f-fee787130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近被迫击炮弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-live/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-goes-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5b18-d65e-a9cf-dfb8da4c0000</link><description>黎巴嫩报道：该国南部的车辆遭到空袭 ■ 叙利亚：飞向大马士革地区的以色列导弹被击落 ■ 以色列军方公布了在北部被杀士兵的姓名 ■ 哈马斯高级官员称其坚持停战提议</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 02:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-live/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-goes-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5b18-d65e-a9cf-dfb8da4c0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：如果拉法继续入侵美国将停止向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-continues-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5a44-d9a0-a38f-fe67a68a0000</link><description>美国总统在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时表示，他告诉总理内塔尼亚胡，如果以色列进入加沙人口中心，将不会得到美国的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 22:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-continues-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5a44-d9a0-a38f-fe67a68a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军前司令：以色列必须停止加沙战争以确保人质获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/former-idf-chief-israel-must-halt-gaza-war-to-secure-release-of-hostages/0000018f-5a15-d65e-a9cf-dfb57e5c0000</link><description>在周三播出的采访中，阿维夫·科查维还承认，以色列在 10 月 7 日之前未能认识到哈马斯是一个生存威胁</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/former-idf-chief-israel-must-halt-gaza-war-to-secure-release-of-hostages/0000018f-5a15-d65e-a9cf-dfb57e5c0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔批准晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的以色列警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-approves-promotion-of-police-officer-under-probe-for-violence-against-protesters/0000018f-59ce-d348-a7bf-ffef6bc10000</link><description>梅厄·苏伊萨（Meir Suissa）目前因多起暴力事件（包括对以色列抗议者使用眩晕手榴弹）而受到以色列警察内部调查部门的调查，他已被晋升为特拉维夫南部地区负责人，立即生效</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-approves-promotion-of-police-officer-under-probe-for-violence-against-protesters/0000018f-59ce-d348-a7bf-ffef6bc10000</guid></item><item><title>官方律师称，内塔尼亚胡在欺诈案中没有询问礼物的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-ask-about-legality-of-gifts-in-fraud-case-official-counsel-says/0000018f-59c2-d0ec-a9cf-dfdfc5a70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的辩护律师称他的法律顾问“有偏见”，因为内塔尼亚胡作证说总理直到 2018 年才就“朋友的礼物”问题与她接触，因此法官选择不干预。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-ask-about-legality-of-gifts-in-fraud-case-official-counsel-says/0000018f-59c2-d0ec-a9cf-dfdfc5a70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登选择冻结向以色列运送炸弹不会让任何人满意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-08/ty-article/.highlight/bidens-choice-to-freeze-bombs-delivery-to-israel-will-please-no-one/0000018f-5964-d9a0-a38f-fd67f9230000</link><description>这是一个值得注意的时刻