ael-thats-heartbreaking-and-dangerous/0000018f-5821-d0ec-a9cf-de3face30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 215 天：官员表示，以色列将把谈判小组留在开罗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-215-israel-to-keep-negotiation-team-in-cairo-officials-says/0000018f-591f-d0ec-a9cf-df1f94cd0001</link><description>国防部长奥斯汀证实美国正在暂停向以色列运送特定武器 ■ 官员称，以色列认为停战谈判没有取得突破的迹象，但仍将代表团留在开罗 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡会见中央情报局局长伯恩斯 ■ 凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点重新开放接受人道主义援助 ■ 访问黎巴嫩边境，以色列国防部长称“这里的任务尚未完成” ■ 战争进入 215 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:01:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-215-israel-to-keep-negotiation-team-in-cairo-officials-says/0000018f-591f-d0ec-a9cf-df1f94cd0001</guid></item><item><title>“现在不是庆祝的时候”：特拉维夫市长在加沙战争中取消一年一度的骄傲游行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/this-isnt-time-for-celebrations-tel-aviv-mayor-calls-off-pride-parade-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-58d6-d6a5-a5ff-daf687db0000</link><description>特拉维夫市长在宣布取消活动时表示，“悲伤的范围每天都在扩大，我们正处于以色列国最困难的时期之一”。耶路撒冷的游行也是抗议活动，将于5月30日照常举行</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 16:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/this-isnt-time-for-celebrations-tel-aviv-mayor-calls-off-pride-parade-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-58d6-d6a5-a5ff-daf687db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列已经成为国际社会的贱民。以色列人关心吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-starting-to-feel-what-its-like-to-be-an-international-pariah/0000018f-5842-dd02-adbf-7fcbf63e0000</link><description>从贸易、学术到外交，以色列正面临着日益加剧的国际孤立。紧迫的问题是以色列人是否会继续扭转加沙战争的后果，或者改变路线</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 16:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-are-starting-to-feel-what-its-like-to-be-an-international-pariah/0000018f-5842-dd02-adbf-7fcbf63e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列特种部队军官在约旦河西岸袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-raid/0000018f-5894-d6a5-a5ff-dab402a60000</link><description>28 岁的首席督察耶塔夫·列夫·哈利维 (Yetav Lev Halevy) 是以色列警察特种反恐部队的指挥官。他在对哈马斯恐怖分子活动场所的一次突袭中受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 15:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-raid/0000018f-5894-d6a5-a5ff-dab402a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军获得的新材料证实两名以色列人质死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/deaths-of-two-israeli-hostages-confirmed-on-basis-of-new-material-obtained-by-idf/0000018f-5882-d348-a7bf-feabc4250000</link><description>负责检查人质状况的医疗委员会的一名成员表示，迄今为止，委员会已经确认了 30 多名此前被认为是人质的人的死亡：他们&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 14:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/deaths-of-two-israeli-hostages-confirmed-on-basis-of-new-material-obtained-by-idf/0000018f-5882-d348-a7bf-feabc4250000</guid></item><item><title>联合航空将以色列航班停飞期限延长至五月底，以色列航空唯一承运人为美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-extends-suspension-of-israel-flights-leaving-el-al-sole-carrier-to-u-s/0000018f-5845-dfc1-adbf-59f53b3b0000</link><description>该航空公司此前已暂停运营至5月9日。已通知旅行社，5月31日之前的航班将被取消</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 14:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-extends-suspension-of-israel-flights-leaving-el-al-sole-carrier-to-u-s/0000018f-5845-dfc1-adbf-59f53b3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防巨头IAI无意中透露了其最大的外国客户：印度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</link><description>事实证明，去年印度占以色列航空航天工业公司出口收入的四分之一。以色列公司的年度报告中还披露了阿塞拜疆和摩洛哥的详细信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</guid></item></channel></rss>